* Iron Raptor suddenly snapped to attention when the door to the CR chamber 
suddenly activated, Firearm running into the room carrying something...or 
someone.
She took a quick look towards Inu before turning towards Firearm abruptly.*

" Hay! Wait up! What's wrong?!"

* Iron Raptor suddenly became worried, there was something wrong here and 
she wasn't really sure if she wanted to find out.
But then she suddenly thought about Prowl and wondered how he was doing, but 
then her spark suddenly jumped into her throat.
She suddenly gets a clear image of what Firearm was carrying, PROWL!!!
Iron Raptor ran up beside Firearm.*

" What happened?!!

* Her voice was fuul of concern as she looks at Prowl's body.
She had a feeling that something bad would happen!*
